latestIgtvVideos.caption:
And that's a wrap! As COP27 draws to a close we hope that global leaders will take the necessary steps to involve young people in climate negotiations. 

Our Global Head of Activism Alice Mazzola says “Young people work tirelessly to raise their voices on the issues they care about, the climate emergency is just one area where they are leading the fight on an issue that affects us all. 

The decisions we make now about our planet will affect their future, so intergenerational collaboration is key to ensuring the world that future generations inherit is good enough.”

 Penny Dalkou, Vasso Balou, Fanni Kiss, Paloma Abril, Isvilaine Silva, Margaret Impraim, Joshua Amponsem

#TheBodyShop #BeSeenBeHeard  #COP27

Calling all EU Citizens! 📣🐰

We have just 1 week left to gather as many signatures as possible to Save Cruelty Free Cosmetics. The future of ALL vegan and cruelty free cosmetics is at risk, and it is down to us to make sure the European Union keeps the promises they made back in 2013. 

🖊️ If you are an EU citizen, check out this video to see how you can sign now! Link in bio. 

📱 If you can’t sign, who do you know that can? Spread the world and send this to 3 friends.
